These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-1::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: epic, musical
The people have 2 different hobbies: fishing, dancing
1. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | epic  | musical |
| Hobby     | dancing | fishing  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-2::.
2 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, chinchilla
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skateboarding, snowboarding
1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2       |
| Pet    | guinea-pig      | chinchilla         |
| Sport   | skateboarding | snowboarding |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, soy-milk
There are 2 different favourite colors: coral, blood-red
1. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | milk   |
| Color       | blood-red  | coral |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-4::.
