.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-5::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: helicopter, jet-ski
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: crime, horror
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |   2    |
| Transport      | helicopter | jet-ski |
| Movie-Genre   | horror        | crime  |

